    {
      "text": "TechnoMage (also called TechnoMage: Return of Eternity, German: TechnoMage: Die Rückkehr der Ewigkeit) is a video game released by German game developer Sunflowers. Technomage was only ever released in PAL territories.\nIt appeared on November 24, 2000, for Windows and on June 29, 2001, for the PlayStation. It was the last own production of the company; in 2002 the internal development department was dissolved.",
